Package bg.sofia.uni.fmi.mjt.dealership.server.command

package bg.sofia.uni.fmi.mjt.dealership.server.command
The command package contains classes and interfaces that define and implement the command pattern used in the application.
Interfaces: Command

Classes: CommandParser
CommandValidator

which are responsible for executing commands in the application.
